str2: To go up, mount, ascend; of things: I rise, spring up, come up. From ana and the base of basis; to go up.

str2: To greet, salute, pay my respects to, welcome. To enfold in the arms, i.e. to salute, to welcome.
The, the definite article. Including the feminine he, and the neuter to in all their inflections; the definite article; the.
From a compound of ek and a derivative of kaleo; a calling out, i.e. a popular meeting, especially a religious congregation.

str2: To go down, come down, either from the sky or from higher land, descend. From kata and the base of basis; to descend.
